%F A382308 a(n) = 2*(Fibonacci(n))^2+4*Fibonacci(n) + 1.
%e A382308 For n=2, the short leg is A382608(2,1) = 3 and the long leg is A382608(2,2) = 4 so the sum of the legs is then a(2) = 3 + 4 = 7.
